::KitKat::

She got up and walked a few paces as the stinger missles hit. She was 
thrown into the air and fell into a ditch 30 feet from where the 
missles hit.  She lay there for a moment.  She breathed heavily.  The 
pain surged through her body and she went into stasis lock.
